title: Dark Circle screening (7/28, 7/29 and 7/31)
instructionText:
We are excited to invite volunteers for an innovative skin study where your participation is as easy as using your smartphone! Simply answer a few brief questions about your skin and lifestyle, then submit a current selfie, all from the comfort of your home. 

Your valuable input will help to gain crucial insights into diverse skin characteristics and develop the next generation of personalized, effective skincare products, allowing you to directly contribute to advancements in beauty science with minimal effort.
label: Dark Circle screening (7/28, 7/29 and 7/31)
